# VLAN DNS Testing Checklist

Use this checklist to verify DNS resolution via Pi-hole + Unbound on each VLAN.
Summary:

Your Pi-hole + Unbound setup is functioning as expected across all tests:

DNS resolution is fast and accurate.

DNSSEC is correctly configured (valid and invalid cases handled).

Recursive queries work as expected with the first lookup taking slightly longer than cached queries.

Blocklists are functioning and blocking requests as expected.

